391
00:33:43,779 --> 00:33:46,099
[SPEAKER_01] Djeta ima šest godina, ne mislim da je tada imao pet.

392
00:33:46,099 --> 00:33:49,460
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, stvarno uče primjerom,

393
00:33:49,460 --> 00:33:51,160
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, a mi nismo možda ni svjesni

394
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:53,799
[SPEAKER_01] koliko oni upijaju i iz toga moramo biti jako pažljivi

395
00:33:53,799 --> 00:33:55,859
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo u svim našim obhođenjima tijekom dana.

396
00:33:55,859 --> 00:33:58,559
[SPEAKER_03] A u toj obiteljskoj molitvi,

397
00:33:58,559 --> 00:34:01,220
[SPEAKER_03] ko, ili ima neko ko to pokreće?

398
00:34:01,220 --> 00:34:02,619
[SPEAKER_03] Je li to podijeljeno u polugama?

399
00:34:02,619 --> 00:34:04,019
[SPEAKER_03] Ili je li bi trebalo biti podijeljeno

400
00:34:04,019 --> 00:34:08,679
[SPEAKER_03] muško u obitelji i uvijek pokreće molitvu?

401
00:34:08,679 --> 00:34:11,420
[SPEAKER_03] Ili to nije tako ili uopće ne treba biti tako?

402
00:34:11,420 --> 00:34:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je u našem slučaju,

403
00:34:13,119 --> 00:34:14,639
[SPEAKER_00] dani su nam dosta kaotični,

404
00:34:14,639 --> 00:34:17,239
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda je to, nikad se ne znam kad se moli.

405
00:34:17,239 --> 00:34:18,719
[SPEAKER_00] Najčešće ja podežujem,

406
00:34:18,719 --> 00:34:20,719
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam ja planer ti posebe,

407
00:34:20,719 --> 00:34:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] iako ništa ne mogu planirati trenutno u životu.

408
00:34:23,039 --> 00:34:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] A muž je totalno spontan lik.

409
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:28,420
[SPEAKER_00] No, planiram danas dva sata unaprijed,

410
00:34:28,420 --> 00:34:28,780
[SPEAKER_00] i to je to.

411
00:34:28,780 --> 00:34:31,739
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ja više podežem na tom frontu sad.

412
00:34:31,739 --> 00:34:33,440
[SPEAKER_03] Jelena?

413
00:34:33,440 --> 00:34:34,900
[SPEAKER_02] Pa evo, rekla sam mene,

414
00:34:34,900 --> 00:34:37,480
[SPEAKER_02] sin neki da vam potaknuo kužiš,

415
00:34:37,480 --> 00:34:40,239
[SPEAKER_02] tako da potiču nas i djeca

416
00:34:40,239 --> 00:34:41,699
[SPEAKER_01] od kojih ne očekuješ.

417
00:34:41,699 --> 00:34:44,260
[SPEAKER_01] Pa uglavnom potičemo

418
00:34:44,260 --> 00:34:46,099
[SPEAKER_01] suprugi ja, Ivan i ja.

419
00:34:46,099 --> 00:34:48,239
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je bilo fora kad smo mi počeli

420
00:34:48,239 --> 00:34:49,639
[SPEAKER_01] zajedno molit, kako je to izgledalo.

421
00:34:49,639 --> 00:34:50,599
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je bio kaos.

422
00:34:50,599 --> 00:34:51,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam rekla mužu,

423
00:34:51,980 --> 00:34:54,039
[SPEAKER_01] prije ne znam, kad je bilo deset godina,

424
00:34:54,039 --> 00:34:54,760
[SPEAKER_01] gled, znaš šta,

425
00:34:54,760 --> 00:34:56,300
[SPEAKER_01] mogli bi mi zajedno moliti.

426
00:34:56,300 --> 00:34:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] A meni vijeli, kako to misliš zajedno?

427
00:34:58,000 --> 00:34:58,780
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ti moliš za sebe?

428
00:34:58,780 --> 00:34:59,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ja molim za sebe,

429
00:34:59,559 --> 00:35:00,159
[SPEAKER_01] ne, zajedno.

430
00:35:00,159 --> 00:35:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vijelim, pa ne, ono, baš zajedno.

431
00:35:02,380 --> 00:35:04,400
[SPEAKER_01] I kožu vam, pa šta ćemo moliti zajedno?

432
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:06,019
[SPEAKER_01] Razumim, zašto bi mi molili zajedno?

433
00:35:06,099 --> 00:35:08,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, i onda smo mi počeli moliti.

434
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:11,900
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, baš, ono, baš, ja sam forsirala, jel?

435
00:35:11,900 --> 00:35:13,920
[SPEAKER_01] I to je bilo jako neobično.

436
00:35:13,920 --> 00:35:15,059
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, on nije znao di bi gledala.

437
00:35:15,059 --> 00:35:17,059
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nije znao di bi gledala šta bi s rukama, šta bi.

438
00:35:17,059 --> 00:35:18,619
[SPEAKER_01] To je baš bilo neobično.

439
00:35:18,619 --> 00:35:20,139
[SPEAKER_01] Danas im je to toliko prirodna stvar,

440
00:35:20,139 --> 00:35:22,699
[SPEAKER_01] da nam je neobično kad ne molimo u danu zajedno, jel?

441
00:35:23,099 --> 00:35:25,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, vijelim, to je možda za savjet svima onima

442
00:35:25,599 --> 00:35:28,820
[SPEAKER_01] koji ne mole zajedno da se ne trebaju obeshrabriti.

443
00:35:28,820 --> 00:35:31,800
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ako imaju tu nekakvu početnu nelagodupa,

444
00:35:31,800 --> 00:35:34,099
[SPEAKER_01] im je nelagodno pred mužem ili mužu pred ženom,

445
00:35:34,099 --> 00:35:37,420
[SPEAKER_01] da je to nešto što je normalno i što će se prevladati, jel?

446
00:35:37,420 --> 00:35:42,340
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, evo, nas dvoje uglavnom potičemo, jel?

447
00:35:42,340 --> 00:35:44,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ponekad on, ponekad ja, ali uglavnom mi,

448
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:45,260
[SPEAKER_01] ali, vijelim, dakle, često i djevo.

449
00:35:45,260 --> 00:35:47,300
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, naši su cure sad već velike, 16 godina,

450
00:35:47,300 --> 00:35:49,079
[SPEAKER_01] one su stvarno duboko u molitvi

451
00:35:49,079 --> 00:35:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ja kad njih vidim kako mole, ja kažem, Bože, ono,

452
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:56,559
[SPEAKER_01] di bi bila, ne znam tako, sa 16 godina.

453
00:35:56,559 --> 00:35:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, ne, to stvarno je baš za primjer.

454
00:35:59,619 --> 00:36:00,860
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je za primjer kao mami.

455
00:36:00,860 --> 00:36:04,039
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da nas one često i svojim primjerom znaju potaknuti,

456
00:36:04,039 --> 00:36:06,519
[SPEAKER_01] a i one reći, e, gle, znaš šta, sad nam je,

457
00:36:06,519 --> 00:36:07,960
[SPEAKER_01] kreće nam, ne znam, devetnica,

458
00:36:07,960 --> 00:36:09,760
[SPEAKER_01] jer nam ja sad bavio šućer rekla,

459
00:36:09,760 --> 00:36:12,239
[SPEAKER_01] ko će mi se pridružiti u, ne znam,

460
00:36:12,239 --> 00:36:14,199
[SPEAKER_01] procesi za gospu karmalsku, ne?

461
00:36:14,199 --> 00:36:16,239
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, kao, pa, idemo svi, ne?

462
00:36:16,239 --> 00:36:19,760
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ona je to izrekla, ne znajući da smo se mi već to dogovorili,

463
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:21,579
[SPEAKER_01] tako da evo, baš potiču i djeca.

464
00:36:21,579 --> 00:36:25,539
[SPEAKER_03] Oba dve ste rekli da ste članice zajednica.

465
00:36:25,539 --> 00:36:27,619
[SPEAKER_03] Tisi članica, Bože,

466
00:36:27,619 --> 00:36:29,739
[SPEAKER_03] pobjede tisi članica obiteljske zajednice.

467
00:36:29,739 --> 00:36:31,320
[SPEAKER_03] Pored svega što radite,

468
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:33,019
[SPEAKER_03] uloga koje imate i obave za koje imate.

469
00:36:33,019 --> 00:36:35,440
[SPEAKER_03] Kaj vam to još treba?

470
00:36:35,440 --> 00:36:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] E, tebi treba.

471
00:36:39,239 --> 00:36:42,239
[SPEAKER_02] Jel ti milo ili nije milo?

472
00:36:42,239 --> 00:36:43,079
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim da ti je milo.

473
00:36:43,079 --> 00:36:46,960
[SPEAKER_02] Jel ti doživljavaš to ko teret?

474
00:36:46,960 --> 00:36:48,099
[SPEAKER_02] Ja ne doživljavam ko teret.

475
00:36:48,099 --> 00:36:49,360
[SPEAKER_02] Ja to doživljam ko milost.

476
00:36:49,360 --> 00:36:51,360
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim, sve više, pazi, sve više,

477
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:52,739
[SPEAKER_02] baš ko milost da ne ko teret.

478
00:36:52,739 --> 00:36:55,099
[SPEAKER_03] Pa dobro, ali sigurno se nađete u situaciju

479
00:36:55,099 --> 00:36:58,980
[SPEAKER_03] kojoj imate sigurno da vam se ne da otić,

480
00:36:58,980 --> 00:37:00,340
[SPEAKER_03] da vam je teško otić

481
00:37:00,340 --> 00:37:03,119
[SPEAKER_03] i da imate dobro opravdanje

482
00:37:03,119 --> 00:37:04,840
[SPEAKER_03] za koje ne otići na, ne znam,

483
00:37:04,840 --> 00:37:06,739
[SPEAKER_03] jednom tjedno imamo to.

484
00:37:06,739 --> 00:37:09,500
[SPEAKER_03] Ne mogu, umoram sam, ne moram

485
00:37:09,500 --> 00:37:11,280
[SPEAKER_03] i evo imam dobar razlog za ne.

486
00:37:11,280 --> 00:37:12,840
[SPEAKER_03] Zaka ipak otićete?

487
00:37:12,840 --> 00:37:15,739
[SPEAKER_03] Može biti neko, nevam,

488
00:37:15,739 --> 00:37:17,840
[SPEAKER_03] za posvjedočit, možda, nemam pojma.

489
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:18,659
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, mogu joj ako, jel?

490
00:37:18,659 --> 00:37:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] Da, daj, daj, daj.

491
00:37:19,460 --> 00:37:20,840
[SPEAKER_00] Jel mi treba?

492
00:37:20,840 --> 00:37:22,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, treba, ne stignem, ne mogu,

493
00:37:22,679 --> 00:37:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] ne imam načina.

494
00:37:23,559 --> 00:37:25,119
[SPEAKER_00] Jel mi treba?

495
00:37:25,119 --> 00:37:26,199
[SPEAKER_00] Zapravo, treba.

496
00:37:26,199 --> 00:37:29,480
[SPEAKER_00] Zato jer prva stvar,

497
00:37:29,599 --> 00:37:31,059
[SPEAKER_00] kad te Bog stavi na mjesto služenja

498
00:37:31,059 --> 00:37:31,800
[SPEAKER_00] njegovom kraljestu,

499
00:37:31,800 --> 00:37:32,500
[SPEAKER_00] ti si siguran.

500
00:37:32,500 --> 00:37:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si rješen, ti si u njegovoj volji.

501
00:37:34,619 --> 00:37:36,500
[SPEAKER_00] I onda se ne sekiraš ni o čemu.

502
00:37:36,500 --> 00:37:37,579
[SPEAKER_00] Nije o djeci, ni o kući,

503
00:37:37,579 --> 00:37:38,519
[SPEAKER_00] ni o ovim, ni o onom,

504
00:37:38,519 --> 00:37:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] ni o poslovima, ni o čemu.

505
00:37:39,519 --> 00:37:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] Jer si ti na pravom mjestu.

506
00:37:41,579 --> 00:37:42,639
[SPEAKER_00] A druga stvar,

507
00:37:42,639 --> 00:37:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] ja ako volim baš,

508
00:37:43,619 --> 00:37:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] ti blagoslove Božje pobjede

509
00:37:45,019 --> 00:37:45,840
[SPEAKER_00] i naše zajednice

510
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:46,840
[SPEAKER_00] koji se obilno izljevaju

511
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:47,940
[SPEAKER_00] na našu obitelj,

512
00:37:47,940 --> 00:37:48,920
[SPEAKER_00] na svim frontama.

513
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:49,960
[SPEAKER_00] I to baš, ono,

514
00:37:49,960 --> 00:37:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] više puta sam osvjetila

515
00:37:51,119 --> 00:37:51,719
[SPEAKER_00] i osjećam.

516
00:37:59,599 --> 00:38:04,559
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je zanimljivo

517
00:38:04,559 --> 00:38:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] kako ja zapravo

518
00:38:06,480 --> 00:38:09,239
[SPEAKER_01] sam ušla u zajednicu,

519
00:38:09,239 --> 00:38:11,300
[SPEAKER_01] a nisam imala neku žarku

520
00:38:11,300 --> 00:38:11,940
[SPEAKER_01] unutarnju želju

521
00:38:11,940 --> 00:38:13,039
[SPEAKER_01] da uđem uopće u zajednicu.

522
00:38:13,039 --> 00:38:13,699
[SPEAKER_01] Znači kad sam ušla

523
00:38:13,699 --> 00:38:14,579
[SPEAKER_01] prije 9 godina.

524
00:38:14,579 --> 00:38:15,300
[SPEAKER_03] Koncep zajednice.

525
00:38:15,300 --> 00:38:16,219
[SPEAKER_01] Koncep zajednice, da, da.

526
00:38:16,219 --> 00:38:18,400
[SPEAKER_01] Znači ja nisam imala čežnju.

527
00:38:18,400 --> 00:38:19,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam imala čežnju,

528
00:38:19,719 --> 00:38:21,320
[SPEAKER_01] imali smo i muži,

529
00:38:21,320 --> 00:38:22,539
[SPEAKER_01] ja i puno smo o tome razgovarali

530
00:38:22,539 --> 00:38:23,440
[SPEAKER_01] kad smo došli na Arun.

531
00:38:24,239 --> 00:38:25,519
[SPEAKER_01] Gleda, sad došli smo u novu župu.

532
00:38:25,519 --> 00:38:27,059
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo zapravo uvijek bili

533
00:38:27,059 --> 00:38:29,480
[SPEAKER_01] kao u nekakvim neformalnim zajednicama.

534
00:38:29,480 --> 00:38:30,659
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, one nisu bile formalne,

535
00:38:30,659 --> 00:38:31,659
[SPEAKER_01] nisu imale svoje ime,

536
00:38:31,659 --> 00:38:32,940
[SPEAKER_01] ali je, dakle, to trebalo

537
00:38:32,940 --> 00:38:33,699
[SPEAKER_01] nekoliko godina,

538
00:38:33,699 --> 00:38:35,579
[SPEAKER_01] nekakva skupina mladih i župe

539
00:38:35,579 --> 00:38:36,800
[SPEAKER_01] koja se, dakle, družila,

540
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:38,460
[SPEAKER_01] dijelovala, služila u župi i tako,

541
00:38:38,460 --> 00:38:39,320
[SPEAKER_01] ali nije bila formalna,

542
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:40,980
[SPEAKER_01] ali zapravo je isto bila nekakva zajednica.

543
00:38:40,980 --> 00:38:42,639
[SPEAKER_01] I onda kad smo se preselili,

544
00:38:42,639 --> 00:38:44,059
[SPEAKER_01] s obzirom da smo mi dugo zajedno,

545
00:38:44,059 --> 00:38:45,980
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda imamo i taj dio života zajednički, ne.

546
00:38:47,400 --> 00:38:48,860
[SPEAKER_01] Kad smo se preselili na Arun,

547
00:38:48,860 --> 00:38:52,039
[SPEAKER_01] onda, dakle, nismo,

548
00:38:52,039 --> 00:38:53,280
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, ni on i ja nismo imali

549
00:38:53,280 --> 00:38:55,400
[SPEAKER_01] nikakvu želju za ući u nikakvu zajednicu.

550
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:57,219
[SPEAKER_01] Nama je bila želja

551
00:38:57,219 --> 00:38:59,360
[SPEAKER_01] biti povezan sa župnom zajednicom.

552
00:38:59,360 --> 00:39:00,800
[SPEAKER_01] To nam je stvarno bila želja.

553
00:39:00,800 --> 00:39:03,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, nismo znali kako joj ostvariti.

554
00:39:03,699 --> 00:39:04,719
[SPEAKER_01] Gledaj, dolaziš na misu,

555
00:39:04,719 --> 00:39:05,739
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda, ok, paajde,

556
00:39:05,739 --> 00:39:06,980
[SPEAKER_01] nekoga znaš, postaneš malo,

557
00:39:06,980 --> 00:39:08,840
[SPEAKER_01] pa popričaš, pa popiješ kavu i tako.

558
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:12,159
[SPEAKER_01] I mi smo zapravo ušli u zajednicu

559
00:39:12,159 --> 00:39:13,480
[SPEAKER_01] na poziv Dom Filipa,

560
00:39:13,480 --> 00:39:15,260
[SPEAKER_01] prekrasnog jednog svećanika

561
00:39:15,260 --> 00:39:16,159
[SPEAKER_01] koji je bio na Arunu.

562
00:39:16,159 --> 00:39:19,940
[SPEAKER_01] I ušli smo nakon opetovanih poziva.

563
00:39:19,940 --> 00:39:21,039
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, nismo ušli odmah.

564
00:39:21,039 --> 00:39:22,900
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, on je nas nekoliko puta zvao

565
00:39:22,900 --> 00:39:24,480
[SPEAKER_01] i bilo je ono kao, gle,

566
00:39:24,480 --> 00:39:26,420
[SPEAKER_01] ja radim do osam zajednica,

567
00:39:26,420 --> 00:39:28,260
[SPEAKER_01] ima svoj susret tada imala u sedam.

568
00:39:28,260 --> 00:39:30,300
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, ono, uopće nema smisla

569
00:39:30,300 --> 00:39:32,019
[SPEAKER_01] da ja sada dolazim u pola devet,

570
00:39:32,019 --> 00:39:33,760
[SPEAKER_01] tamo na nekak podruženje poslije,

571
00:39:33,760 --> 00:39:35,320
[SPEAKER_01] ako ne mogu stići na misu

572
00:39:35,320 --> 00:39:37,559
[SPEAKER_01] ili dakle na nekakav formativni susret i tako.

573
00:39:37,559 --> 00:39:39,260
[SPEAKER_01] I on je bio uporan, uporan, uporan

574
00:39:39,260 --> 00:39:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] i mi smo se na kraju priključili zajednici.

575
00:39:45,260 --> 00:39:49,599
[SPEAKER_01] Pa dobro, okej, evo, ući ćemo u zajednicu

576
00:39:49,599 --> 00:39:52,659
[SPEAKER_01] jer će to meni pomoći za moj osobni odnos s Bogom,

577
00:39:52,659 --> 00:39:54,199
[SPEAKER_01] za moj, dakle, duhovni rast.

578
00:39:54,199 --> 00:39:57,099
[SPEAKER_01] I to je i dan danas, dakle, cilj svakog onoga

579
00:39:57,099 --> 00:39:58,159
[SPEAKER_01] koji u bilo koje zajednici,

580
00:39:58,159 --> 00:40:02,480
[SPEAKER_01] znači da ti svoj osobni odnos s Bogom poboljšavaš.

581
00:40:02,480 --> 00:40:04,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je samo jedan od ciljeva.

582
00:40:04,619 --> 00:40:07,739
[SPEAKER_01] I zanimljivo mi je kako zapravo ja spoznajem

583
00:40:07,739 --> 00:40:10,159
[SPEAKER_01] kako sada skroz drugo, na drugi način,

584
00:40:10,260 --> 00:40:12,219
[SPEAKER_01] gledam zapravo svoje prisustvo u zajednici.

585
00:40:12,219 --> 00:40:15,500
[SPEAKER_01] Znači ja sada, dakle, sam svjesna

586
00:40:15,500 --> 00:40:19,480
[SPEAKER_01] da je Bog, dakle, opremio Dom Filipa

587
00:40:19,480 --> 00:40:21,099
[SPEAKER_01] sa različitim sposobnostima,

588
00:40:21,099 --> 00:40:24,699
[SPEAKER_01] različitim vrlinama, različitim darobima,

589
00:40:24,699 --> 00:40:26,400
[SPEAKER_01] ne zbog njega samoga,

590
00:40:26,400 --> 00:40:28,440
[SPEAKER_01] nego da bi on mogao mene pozvati,

591
00:40:28,440 --> 00:40:31,119
[SPEAKER_01] a mene je sada opremio da bi ja mogla drugog pozvati.

592
00:40:31,119 --> 00:40:33,500
[SPEAKER_01] I ovo što danas radim je isto to zapravo.

593
00:40:33,500 --> 00:40:34,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sad sebe dajem, jel?

594
00:40:34,800 --> 00:40:36,460
[SPEAKER_01] Sve ono što je meni, dragi Bog, dao,

595
00:40:36,460 --> 00:40:37,719
[SPEAKER_01] ja sada želim to dati dalje.

596
00:40:38,260 --> 00:40:39,980
[SPEAKER_01] I treća stvar, služenje.

597
00:40:39,980 --> 00:40:42,719
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mi smo sad odnedavno imamo

598
00:40:42,719 --> 00:40:44,059
[SPEAKER_01] malo aktivnije službe,

599
00:40:44,059 --> 00:40:44,840
[SPEAKER_01] imali smo ih i prije,

600
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:46,099
[SPEAKER_01] ali mi smo svi, mislim,

601
00:40:46,099 --> 00:40:47,940
[SPEAKER_01] drugačije je malo sada koncept.

602
00:40:47,940 --> 00:40:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] I sad smo mi svi, dakle, u službama.

603
00:40:49,960 --> 00:40:51,219
[SPEAKER_01] I meni je silo, pa stvarno,

604
00:40:51,219 --> 00:40:52,860
[SPEAKER_01] gled, biti u službi znači služiti, jel?

605
00:40:52,860 --> 00:40:54,539
[SPEAKER_01] I ja sam čerima znala govoriti

606
00:40:54,539 --> 00:40:55,380
[SPEAKER_01] kako one sviraju.

607
00:40:55,380 --> 00:40:57,679
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je njima znala u jednom periodu

608
00:40:57,679 --> 00:41:00,280
[SPEAKER_01] biti, ono, tog puberteta.

609
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:01,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ja, gledaš kaj, danas imam puno za učiti,

610
00:41:01,800 --> 00:41:02,460
[SPEAKER_01] pa mi je teško,

611
00:41:08,260 --> 00:41:10,480
[SPEAKER_01] gled, koliko nam je Bog dao milosti u životu.

612
00:41:10,480 --> 00:41:12,340
[SPEAKER_01] To je način da mi Bogu zahvalimo.

613
00:41:12,340 --> 00:41:14,679
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, tako da, treća stvar je ta zahvala.

614
00:41:14,679 --> 00:41:16,320
[SPEAKER_01] Zapravo, ja sa tim služenjem

615
00:41:16,320 --> 00:41:19,360
[SPEAKER_01] stvarno, evo, Bogu želim zahvaliti.

616
00:41:19,360 --> 00:41:20,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, baš mu želim zahvaliti

617
00:41:20,480 --> 00:41:22,059
[SPEAKER_01] za sve milosti koje mi je dao, jel?

618
00:41:22,059 --> 00:41:23,079
[SPEAKER_01] I koje mi daje dalje.

619
00:41:23,079 --> 00:41:24,980
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, evo, skroz,

620
00:41:24,980 --> 00:41:26,619
[SPEAKER_01] na drugačiji način doživljavam

621
00:41:26,619 --> 00:41:28,159
[SPEAKER_01] svoje prisutnost u zajednici

622
00:41:28,159 --> 00:41:29,460
[SPEAKER_01] nego prije, a da mi treba,

623
00:41:29,460 --> 00:41:30,420
[SPEAKER_01] definitivno mi treba,

624
00:41:30,420 --> 00:41:34,300
[SPEAKER_01] da mi, da sam obogačena,

625
00:41:34,460 --> 00:41:35,599
[SPEAKER_01] definitivno sam obogućena,

626
00:41:35,599 --> 00:41:36,639
[SPEAKER_01] da je nekada teško

627
00:41:36,639 --> 00:41:37,679
[SPEAKER_01] i naporno je,

628
00:41:37,679 --> 00:41:40,079
[SPEAKER_01] da nekada imaš i napasti imaš,

629
00:41:40,079 --> 00:41:41,360
[SPEAKER_01] ali to je nešto što,

630
00:41:41,360 --> 00:41:41,840
[SPEAKER_01] uopće,

631
00:41:41,840 --> 00:41:44,300
[SPEAKER_01] tem se uopće više ne čudim.

632
00:41:44,300 --> 00:41:45,719
[SPEAKER_03] A daj sad, kad već pričam

633
00:41:45,719 --> 00:41:46,420
[SPEAKER_03] o tim nejakvim,

634
00:41:46,420 --> 00:41:47,840
[SPEAKER_03] to su sad već nejakve stvari,

635
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:49,500
[SPEAKER_03] Ana, ti si u BPU koliko?

636
00:41:49,500 --> 00:41:52,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam, četiri, pet godina,

637
00:41:52,519 --> 00:41:53,260
[SPEAKER_00] ne pojmo.

638
00:41:53,260 --> 00:41:54,920
[SPEAKER_03] Znači, ti si u bisniskoj zajednici

639
00:41:54,920 --> 00:41:55,420
[SPEAKER_03] deset godina,

640
00:41:55,420 --> 00:41:56,019
[SPEAKER_03] devet godina.

641
00:41:56,019 --> 00:41:56,619
[SPEAKER_00] Devet, deset, da.

642
00:41:56,619 --> 00:41:57,579
[SPEAKER_03] To su sad nejakve stvari

643
00:41:57,579 --> 00:41:58,940
[SPEAKER_03] koje očito nisu samo prolazne

644
00:41:58,940 --> 00:41:59,679
[SPEAKER_03] i nisu hirevi.

645
00:42:04,460 --> 00:42:06,340
[SPEAKER_03] članica slavljeničke službe,

646
00:42:06,340 --> 00:42:09,219
[SPEAKER_03] okej, ja znam koliko si bit na BPU,

647
00:42:09,219 --> 00:42:12,139
[SPEAKER_03] s obzirom da ste aktivni u crkvi

648
00:42:12,139 --> 00:42:13,519
[SPEAKER_03] na konkretan način,

649
00:42:13,519 --> 00:42:15,500
[SPEAKER_03] s obzirom da imate nekakve službe

650
00:42:15,500 --> 00:42:18,159
[SPEAKER_03] na mjestima gdje ste se odlučile davati,

651
00:42:18,159 --> 00:42:23,139
[SPEAKER_03] jel vi imate nekakav problem

652
00:42:23,139 --> 00:42:25,420
[SPEAKER_03] s tim da je crkva,

653
00:42:25,420 --> 00:42:28,219
[SPEAKER_03] barem na van,

654
00:42:28,219 --> 00:42:29,920
[SPEAKER_03] orijentirana dosta patriarchalno?

655
00:42:29,920 --> 00:42:30,760
[SPEAKER_03] Recimo, pogledu,

656
00:42:30,760 --> 00:42:33,019
[SPEAKER_03] svećenice su samo muškarci

657
00:42:33,019 --> 00:42:34,840
[SPEAKER_03] i sve je nekak tako malo patriarchalno.

658
00:42:34,840 --> 00:42:37,519
[SPEAKER_03] Jer vama to stvara nekako nelagodno.

659
00:42:37,519 --> 00:42:38,579
[SPEAKER_03] Ne mislim sad teološki,

660
00:42:38,579 --> 00:42:40,239
[SPEAKER_03] tu nema naravno rasprave,

661
00:42:40,239 --> 00:42:43,320
[SPEAKER_03] ali jel vi imate nekakav osjećaj,

662
00:42:43,320 --> 00:42:44,320
[SPEAKER_03] ne znam, manje vrijednosti

663
00:42:44,320 --> 00:42:45,320
[SPEAKER_03] da bi htjeli da nešto drugo,

664
00:42:45,320 --> 00:42:47,380
[SPEAKER_03] da bi htjeli, ne znam,

665
00:42:47,380 --> 00:42:49,840
[SPEAKER_03] nekako veće važnost, nešto,

666
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:50,260
[SPEAKER_03] bilo što.

667
00:42:50,260 --> 00:42:52,079
[SPEAKER_03] Znači, kako se osjećate

668
00:42:52,079 --> 00:42:52,679
[SPEAKER_03] po tom pitanju?

669
00:42:52,679 --> 00:42:54,300
[SPEAKER_03] Ma ja se sviđa skroz normalno.

670
00:42:54,300 --> 00:42:56,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne mislim da je to tako.

671
00:42:56,260 --> 00:42:57,659
[SPEAKER_00] Iako žene,

672
00:42:57,659 --> 00:42:59,239
[SPEAKER_00] jesu na neki način spriječene

673
00:42:59,239 --> 00:43:00,179
[SPEAKER_00] u služenju nekad.

674
00:43:00,179 --> 00:43:01,679
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ja sam nedavno rodila

675
00:43:01,679 --> 00:43:03,159
[SPEAKER_00] i sad ću ja ići na večeslavljenje.

676
00:43:03,159 --> 00:43:04,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam tad bila u rađoni doslovno.

677
00:43:04,719 --> 00:43:06,300
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, ovaj,

678
00:43:06,300 --> 00:43:08,219
[SPEAKER_00] realni život i umjeti

679
00:43:08,219 --> 00:43:09,920
[SPEAKER_00] i žena kao, ono,

680
00:43:09,920 --> 00:43:11,280
[SPEAKER_00] njezin identitet je takav

681
00:43:11,280 --> 00:43:13,099
[SPEAKER_00] da je u jednom periodu života

682
00:43:13,099 --> 00:43:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] mora biti uz djecu,

683
00:43:13,940 --> 00:43:15,460
[SPEAKER_00] ono, blisko i usko povezana.

684
00:43:15,460 --> 00:43:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam mogla ići svirati klavijature

685
00:43:17,199 --> 00:43:18,099
[SPEAKER_00] na večeslavljenje.

686
00:43:18,179 --> 00:43:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, nisam išla na probe,

687
00:43:19,519 --> 00:43:20,380
[SPEAKER_00] nisam tu služila,

688
00:43:20,380 --> 00:43:22,280
[SPEAKER_00] ali to mi je sve skroz normalno.

689
00:43:22,280 --> 00:43:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] Čak bi bilo bolje

690
00:43:24,960 --> 00:43:26,440
[SPEAKER_00] da su svi svirači muški,

691
00:43:26,440 --> 00:43:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] jer oni sigurno mogu doći.

692
00:43:28,039 --> 00:43:29,199
[SPEAKER_00] Jer, ono, žena,

693
00:43:29,199 --> 00:43:30,599
[SPEAKER_00] eno, rodila, eno, trudna,

694
00:43:30,599 --> 00:43:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] eno, dijete, nešto,

695
00:43:32,039 --> 00:43:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] nemam pojma.

696
00:43:32,539 --> 00:43:33,380
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, ono,

697
00:43:33,380 --> 00:43:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] ima to i smisla

698
00:43:35,119 --> 00:43:36,059
[SPEAKER_00] što su muškarci

699
00:43:36,059 --> 00:43:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] u nekim stvarima naprijed.

700
00:43:37,619 --> 00:43:39,119
[SPEAKER_03] Ali nemaš te neki osjećaj

701
00:43:39,119 --> 00:43:39,860
[SPEAKER_03] sad u crkvi

702
00:43:39,860 --> 00:43:42,400
[SPEAKER_03] da si ti, ono,

703
00:43:42,400 --> 00:43:43,659
[SPEAKER_03] da neku nelagod,

704
00:43:43,659 --> 00:43:44,639
[SPEAKER_03] da nemaš neki problem s tim.

705
00:43:44,639 --> 00:43:45,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ma niš.

706
00:43:45,119 --> 00:43:47,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam, evo,

707
00:43:47,320 --> 00:43:48,739
[SPEAKER_01] voditeljica formatske službe

708
00:43:48,739 --> 00:43:49,480
[SPEAKER_01] kao žensko,

709
00:43:49,480 --> 00:43:51,019
[SPEAKER_01] tako da, ono,

710
00:43:51,019 --> 00:43:53,039
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, imate i vi voditeljice,

711
00:43:53,039 --> 00:43:53,539
[SPEAKER_01] je li tako?

712
00:43:53,539 --> 00:43:55,440
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, ja ne vidim,

713
00:43:55,440 --> 00:43:56,039
[SPEAKER_01] recimo, evo,

714
00:43:56,039 --> 00:43:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] u zajednicama uopće ne vidim to,

715
00:43:57,539 --> 00:43:58,280
[SPEAKER_01] ako misliš, dakle,

716
00:43:58,280 --> 00:43:58,760
[SPEAKER_01] svećenstvo,

717
00:43:58,760 --> 00:43:59,900
[SPEAKER_01] znači, to je skroz,

718
00:43:59,900 --> 00:44:00,400
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, teološka priča.

719
00:44:00,400 --> 00:44:01,219
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ok, to je druga,

720
00:44:01,219 --> 00:44:02,460
[SPEAKER_01] to je druga priča,

721
00:44:02,460 --> 00:44:03,119
[SPEAKER_01] tako da, evo,

722
00:44:03,119 --> 00:44:03,539
[SPEAKER_01] ja ne vidim,

723
00:44:03,539 --> 00:44:04,280
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da je iskustvo,

724
00:44:04,280 --> 00:44:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] evo, mislim,

725
00:44:04,739 --> 00:44:05,719
[SPEAKER_01] evo, moje iskustvo,

726
00:44:05,760 --> 00:44:07,340
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, pokazuje da ne da nisam,

727
00:44:07,340 --> 00:44:09,639
[SPEAKER_01] ne da kao žensko nisam,

728
00:44:09,639 --> 00:44:10,400
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj,

729
00:44:10,400 --> 00:44:12,380
[SPEAKER_01] da sam zanemarena,

730
00:44:12,380 --> 00:44:13,320
[SPEAKER_01] nego sam čak, evo,

731
00:44:13,320 --> 00:44:13,820
[SPEAKER_01] i birana.

732
00:44:13,820 --> 00:44:14,860
[SPEAKER_01] Da, to sam mislio,

733
00:44:14,860 --> 00:44:15,659
[SPEAKER_03] nije bila poanta,

734
00:44:15,659 --> 00:44:17,360
[SPEAKER_03] naravno, propitiva se se tiče

735
00:44:17,360 --> 00:44:18,360
[SPEAKER_03] oficijalnih službe,

736
00:44:18,360 --> 00:44:19,659
[SPEAKER_03] nego, ovako, ono,

737
00:44:19,659 --> 00:44:21,719
[SPEAKER_03] uvijek se čini da je muška inicijativa

738
00:44:21,719 --> 00:44:22,579
[SPEAKER_03] ili nešto, pa,

739
00:44:22,579 --> 00:44:23,460
[SPEAKER_03] da, da,

740
00:44:23,460 --> 00:44:23,619
[SPEAKER_03] ok.

741
00:44:23,619 --> 00:44:26,340
[SPEAKER_03] Dobro,

742
00:44:27,840 --> 00:44:29,059
[SPEAKER_03] da ću sad pročititi jedan citat,

743
00:44:29,059 --> 00:44:31,719
[SPEAKER_03] pa ćete mi vi reći

744
00:44:31,719 --> 00:44:33,579
[SPEAKER_03] kak se osjećate

745
00:44:33,579 --> 00:44:34,199
[SPEAKER_03] do ga čitam.

746
00:44:34,199 --> 00:44:37,159
[SPEAKER_03] Žene,

747
00:44:37,159 --> 00:44:39,900
[SPEAKER_03] budite podložne vašim muževima

748
00:44:39,900 --> 00:44:40,719
[SPEAKER_03] kao gospodinu,

749
00:44:40,719 --> 00:44:42,820
[SPEAKER_03] jer muž je glava ženi,

750
00:44:42,820 --> 00:44:44,940
[SPEAKER_03] kao što je krist glava crkvi.

751
00:44:44,940 --> 00:44:48,159
[SPEAKER_03] Je li vam to rađo

752
00:44:48,159 --> 00:44:49,519
[SPEAKER_03] nejakom negativnom emocijom?

753
00:44:49,519 --> 00:44:51,840
[SPEAKER_01] Da, zato što nisi pročitati do kraja.

754
00:44:51,840 --> 00:44:54,340
[SPEAKER_03] A ne, ovo sam si samo izvukao.

755
00:44:54,340 --> 00:44:55,079
[SPEAKER_01] Eto, ovo.

756
00:44:55,079 --> 00:44:57,159
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, te možeš izvlačiti sada

757
00:44:57,159 --> 00:44:58,559
[SPEAKER_01] iz konteksta stvari.

758
00:44:58,559 --> 00:45:01,179
[SPEAKER_03] Ok, ali ovo se često u javnosti

759
00:45:01,179 --> 00:45:01,920
[SPEAKER_03] izvlači van.

760
00:45:01,920 --> 00:45:03,599
[SPEAKER_03] Žene, budite podložne svojim muževima.

761
00:45:03,599 --> 00:45:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ali ima nastavak

762
00:45:04,739 --> 00:45:06,139
[SPEAKER_01] i jako je bitno od konteksta.

763
00:45:06,139 --> 00:45:06,820
[SPEAKER_01] Jako.

764
00:45:06,820 --> 00:45:07,039
[SPEAKER_03] Ok.

765
00:45:07,039 --> 00:45:07,920
[SPEAKER_03] Kužiš?

766
00:45:07,920 --> 00:45:09,920
[SPEAKER_03] Daim ti prostor za nastavak

767
00:45:09,920 --> 00:45:12,119
[SPEAKER_03] i automatski pitanje za obje.

768
00:45:12,119 --> 00:45:14,139
[SPEAKER_03] Da li to živite

769
00:45:14,139 --> 00:45:15,039
[SPEAKER_03] i kak?

770
00:45:15,039 --> 00:45:16,480
[SPEAKER_03] Kaj znači ovo živjeto?

771
00:45:16,480 --> 00:45:17,679
[SPEAKER_03] Ako živite to u svojom živom?

772
00:45:17,679 --> 00:45:18,539
[SPEAKER_01] Nastavak je

773
00:45:18,539 --> 00:45:20,460
[SPEAKER_01] a, muževi ljubite svoje žene.

774
00:45:20,460 --> 00:45:20,980
[SPEAKER_01] Je li tako?

775
00:45:20,980 --> 00:45:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] Kao što je krist ljubio crku.

776
00:45:22,159 --> 00:45:23,320
[SPEAKER_01] Je li tako?

777
00:45:23,519 --> 00:45:24,400
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje znam sad na pamet.

778
00:45:24,400 --> 00:45:25,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mislim da je zadnja rečenica

779
00:45:25,940 --> 00:45:26,659
[SPEAKER_01] u pasusu

780
00:45:26,659 --> 00:45:29,219
[SPEAKER_01] muževi ljubite svoje žene

781
00:45:29,219 --> 00:45:30,619
[SPEAKER_01] a žene poštite svoje muževe.

782
00:45:30,619 --> 00:45:32,659
[SPEAKER_01] E, i tu se onda krije zapravo

783
00:45:32,659 --> 00:45:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] taj cijelokupan kontekst.

784
00:45:34,280 --> 00:45:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, apsolutno nema s tim problema.

785
00:45:36,000 --> 00:45:38,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ja osobno to živim.

786
00:45:38,019 --> 00:45:41,079
